SELECT 
    dtt.tenant_id, 
    dtt.token, 
    t.name as WorkspaceName,
    u.username ,
    u.display_name ,
    sum(t.remain_quota) as qutoa,
    sum(t.used_quota)/500000.0 as used_quota 
FROM 
    dify_tenant_tokens dtt
JOIN 
    tokens t 
ON 
    dtt.token = t.key 
join
    users u 
on
    t.user_id = u.id 
GROUP BY 
    dtt.tenant_id, 
    dtt.token, 
    t.name,
    u.username,
    u.display_name
order by
   used_quota desc
